TEXT 3744 -592 Left 2 !.model MYSW SW(Ron=5 Roff=1e9 Vt=0.5 Vh=0)\n.tran 160u\n \n* Precharge all bottoms and top-plate to 0V for 9.9us\nVrst rst 0 PULSE(0 1 0 1n 1n 9.9u 200u)\n \n* ------------------------------------------------\n* MSB BANK (Range 0V to 5V | Target 2.2V)\n* ------------------------------------------------\n* MSB6 (Bit 13): Trial -> 2.5V (Too high! Clear it)\nVmsb6h msb6h 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 19.9u 1 20u 0 160u 0)\nVmsb6l msb6l 0 PWL(0 0 19.9u 0 20u 1 160u 1)\n \n* MSB5 (Bit 12): Trial -> 1.25V (Keep it!)\nVmsb5h msb5h 0 PWL(0 0 19.9u 0 20u 1 160u 1)\nVmsb5l msb5l 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 19.9u 1 20u 0 160u 0)\n \n* MSB4 (Bit 11): Trial -> 1.875V (Keep it!)\nVmsb4h msb4h 0 PWL(0 0 29.9u 0 30u 1 160u 1)\nVmsb4l msb4l 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 29.9u 1 30u 0 160u 0)\n \n* MSB3 (Bit 10): Trial -> 2.1875V (Keep it!)\nVmsb3h msb3h 0 PWL(0 0 39.9u 0 40u 1 160u 1)\nVmsb3l msb3l 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 39.9u 1 40u 0 160u 0)\n \n* MSB2 (Bit 9): Trial -> 2.343V (Too high! Clear it)\nVmsb2h msb2h 0 PWL(0 0 49.9u 0 50u 1 59.9u 1 60u 0 160u 0)\nVmsb2l msb2l 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 49.9u 1 50u 0 59.9u 0 60u 1 160u 1)\n \n* MSB1 (Bit 8): Trial -> 2.265V (Too high! Clear it)\nVmsb1h msb1h 0 PWL(0 0 59.9u 0 60u 1 69.9u 1 70u 0 160u 0)\nVmsb1l msb1l 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 59.9u 1 60u 0 69.9u 0 70u 1 160u 1)\n \n* MSB0 (Bit 7): Trial -> 2.226V (Too high! Clear it)\nVmsb0h msb0h 0 PWL(0 0 69.9u 0 70u 1 79.9u 1 80u 0 160u 0)\nVmsb0l msb0l 0 PWL(0 0 9.9u 0 10u 1 69.9u 1 70u 0 79.9u 0 80u 1 160u 1)\n \n* (Remaining LSB trials omitted for brevity, but pattern is the same)
